io.libsoft.contactcard.service

Class TextProcessorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.libsoft.contactcard.service.TextProcessorService

  • public class TextProcessorService
extends Object
    Text processing class. Names are checked against a database of names. Emails are parsed from the rawtext via regex patterns. Phone numbers are parsed via regex patterns.
